Package: superassp
Type: Package
Title: A speech signal processing using various framworks using a wrassp-like interface
Version: 0.7.3
Date: 2025-10-24
Authors@R:
    person("Fredrik", "Nylén", email = "fredrik.nylen@umu.se", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Fredrik Nylén <fredrik.nylen@umu.se>
Description: This package bundles together routines that utilizes python, Praat/parsemouth, or Matlab 
  to do the signal processing. The output of the original routines are then
  wrapped into a common interface that outputs an SSFF file or returns a wrassp 
  compatible AsspDataObj object.
